&lt;p&gt;If for a specific reason you can&amp;#8217;t upgrade to 9.1.1, we also included the security fixes to our branches from 2.9 to 8.0. Here&amp;#8217;s the list of the available downloads for the corresponding tags, you can also find on our &lt;a href=&quot;https://wordpress.org/plugins/buddypress/advanced/&quot;&gt;WordPress.org Directory Advanced page:&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;



